    <item>
      <title></title>
      <link>/authors/xpsong/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Apr 2016 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/authors/xpsong/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello, my name is Xiao Ping (XP) and I&amp;rsquo;m working as part of a research group at the Future Cities Laboratory that looks at &amp;lsquo;ecosystem services&amp;rsquo;, which are the benefits that people gain from nature. I&amp;rsquo;m also a doctoral candidate at the National University of Singapore, Department of Architecture. My current work seeks to understand human—environment interactions and recreation behaviour using social media data. Outside of research, I enjoy playing the drums and going for adventure sports. Feel free to contact me via &lt;a href=&#34;#contact&#34;&gt;email&lt;/a&gt; or on social media if you&amp;rsquo;re interested to connect.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
